OL,3,CNeonatal nurse accused of faking CV to
OL,4,Cget a senior job found guilty
OL,6,FA nurse accused of faking her CV to
OL,7,Fget a senior job on a neonatal ward
OL,8,Fhas been found guilty.
OL,10,FTanya Nasir was accused of fabricating
OL,11,Fqualifications and jobs on her CV to
OL,12,Fget a job as a Band 7 Ward Manager on
OL,13,Fthe Neonatal ward at the Princess of
OL,14,FWales Hospital in Bridgend, where she
OL,15,Fworked for 5 months starting in
OL,16,FSeptember 2019.
