OL,3,CNeonatal nurse accused of faking CV to
OL,4,Cget a senior job found guilty
OL,6,FCardiff Crown Court heard that she was
OL,7,Fsuspended from her role after
OL,8,F"inconsistencies" were spotted in her
OL,9,FCV, which led to an NHS counter fraud
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FMs Nasir resigned from her job in
OL,13,FNovember 2021.
OL,15,FDuring the course of the trial, which
OL,16,Flasted more than 4 weeks, the jury
OL,17,Fheard how Tanya Nasir had claimed in
OL,18,Fher job application to have worked as
OL,19,Fa nurse since 2004.
