OL,6,FIn reality, the defendant hadn't
OL,7,Fregistered with the Nursing and
OL,8,FMidwifery Council until February 2014.
OL,10,FMs Nasir also claimed to have been
OL,11,Femployed at the West Herts Hospitals
OL,12,FTrust, as a Band 5 ICU nurse, and at
OL,13,Fthe Chelsea and Westminster NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust, as a neonatal sister
OL,15,F- jobs which, the court heard, she had
OL,16,Fnever held.
