OL,6,FThe jury was also told about fake
OL,7,Fqualifications put forward by Ms
OL,8,FNasir, including degrees in physics
OL,9,Fand astrophysics from Hatfield
OL,10,FPolytechnic (now the university of
OL,11,FHertfordshire).
OL,13,FHer registration document with the
OL,14,FHCPC, which she needed to become a
OL,15,Fward manager, was also false.
