OL,6,FMs Nasir made further false claims to
OL,7,Fhave served with the army, including
OL,8,Fas a Platoon Commander and Combat
OL,9,FMedical Officer in the Royal Medical
OL,10,FCorps, where she said she'd achieved
OL,11,Fthe rank of Major.
OL,13,FBut the truth was that she'd failed
OL,14,Fthe basic fitness test for the army
OL,15,Freserve in 2010. The full extent of
OL,16,Fher military experience was less than
OL,17,Fthree years with the Cadet Force,
OL,18,Fwhere she was a sergeant instructor
OL,19,Fbefore being discharged and struck off
OL,20,Fin 2016.
