OL,6,FThe defendant had never seen active
OL,7,Fservice or been deployed overseas, as
OL,8,Fshe said.
OL,10,FA further claim that she'd obtained a
OL,11,FPGCE from the Royal Military Academy
OL,12,Fat Sandhurst to become a qualified
OL,13,Farmy teaching Instructor was also a
OL,14,Flie.
OL,16,FAn e-mail address for a referee on
OL,17,FNasir's job application in the name of
OL,18,FMatthew Nash-Yearwood - a major in the
OL,19,Fcadet force - was false and in reality
OL,20,Flinked to an account operated by Ms
OL,21,FNasir.
