OL,3,CNeonatal nurse accused of faking CV to
OL,4,Cget a senior job found guilty
OL,6,FTanya Nasir was arrested in April 2021
OL,7,Fby Dyfed Powys Police on suspicion of
OL,8,Ffraud. She told police that all the
OL,9,Finformation she provided on her CV was
OL,10,F"accurate, correct and truthful."
OL,12,FIn 35 hours of interviews with counter-
OL,13,Ffraud officers she stood by her
OL,14,Fclaims, including that during the
OL,15,Fcourse of a 16 year military career,
OL,16,Fshe'd served in Iraq, Sudan and in
OL,17,FAfghanistan, where as a combat medical
OL,18,Fofficer she'd been just 500 metres
OL,19,Ffrom the front line.
