OL,6,FThe court was told that Nasir, who's
OL,7,F45, has four previous convictions for
OL,8,Fbenefit fraud dating back to 2010.
OL,10,FIn a statement issued following the
OL,11,Fverdicts, Paul Mears, Chief Executive
OL,12,Fof Cwm Taf Morgannwg University Health
OL,13,FBoard, said he "welcomed" the jury's
OL,14,Fverdicts, adding: "Ms Nasir
OL,15,Fintentionally deceived employers and
OL,16,Fcolleagues throughout her career, and
OL,17,Fwas finally exposed thanks to the
OL,18,Fvigilance of our teams and processes
OL,19,Fat CTM.
