OL,6,F"During the very short time that Ms
OL,7,FNasir was employed and present in her
OL,8,Flargely office based role at Princess
OL,9,Fof Wales Hospital, her contact with
OL,10,Fbabies and their families was
OL,11,Fextremely minimal.
OL,13,F"Following a thorough internal
OL,14,Finvestigation, we can provide firm
OL,15,Fassurance to families, who were with
OL,16,Fus at that time, that no harm was
OL,17,Fcaused due to Ms Nasir's employment on
OL,18,Fthe neonatal unit."
