OL,6,FGayle Ramsay, of the Crown Prosecution
OL,7,FService, said: "Tanya Nasir
OL,8,Fdeliberately lied about her
OL,9,Fqualifications and employment history
OL,10,Fso that she could gain employment in a
OL,11,Fsenior and sensitive nursing role
OL,12,Fwhere she would be entrusted with the
OL,13,Fresponsibility of caring for newborn
OL,14,Fbabies.
